tool_description:
SkAlpha is an all-encompassing financial API offering real-time news, analysis, and data on a wide array of stocks, ETFs, mutual funds, and commodities, empowering users to make smarter investment decisions.
You will find docs at [Github](https://github.com/lacassef/recodexapicodeexamples/tree/master/sklpha).
name: SkAlpha
title: SkAlpha

api_list.name: topauthors
api_list.description: Get top authors. See it on [Github](https://github.com/lacassef/recodexapicodeexamples/blob/master/sklpha/endpoints/USERS.md#apiskalphatop_authors).
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://skalpha.p.rapidapi.com/api/skalpha/top_authors"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "skalpha.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

import requests

url = "https://skalpha.p.rapidapi.com/api/skalpha/symbols/{symbol}/dividends/payout_ratio_chart"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "skalpha.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
